product.name: Polyphony
product.description: Specifies the simultaneous note capacity of a synthesizer, e.g. polyphonic, multi-timbral

product.name: Synthesis method
product.description: Specifies the method of sound synthesis in electronic instruments, such as virtual analog or modular

product.name: Instrument material
product.description: Identifies the main material used in the construction of a musical instrument, like maple wood or brass
